{"word":"ἀλλότριος","slug":"ἀλλότριος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀλλότριος, α, ον</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄλλος\">ἄλλος</a></el>] ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pert. to\">pert. to</a> belonging to another’, <b><i>another’s</i> <a href='B:520 14:4'>Ro 14:4</a></b> slave; <b><a href='B:540 10:15'>2 Cor 10:15</a></b> work; <b><a href='B:610 5:22'>1 Ti 5:22</a></b> sins; <b><a href='B:510 7:6'>Ac 7:6</a></b> of land that belongs to others and is therefore<b> <i>foreign;</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sim.\">sim.</a> <b><a href='B:650 11:9'>Hb 11:9</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:650 11:34'>11:34</a>.</b> As noun <i>what is not one’s own</i> <b><a href='B:490 16:12'>Lk 16:12</a>.</b> <el>ἀλλοτρίοις <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπίσκοπος\">ἐπίσκοπος</a></el> <i>meddler in other people’s matters</i> <b><a href='B:670 4:15'>1 Pt 4:15</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλλοτριεπίσκοπος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλλόφυλος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}